{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were not allowed to drive at night because all things moving were under-- under Allied airplanes, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you can't see a Swedish flag.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what happened was we pull about by maybe 10, 15 kilometers outside of-- of Dresden.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we're allowed to walk around outside the-- yeah, because you're still sitting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now we're walking around, we're eating our chocolate.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had so much chocolate we got sick and tired.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the way, at the-- at the-- at the Green Valley when I gave a speech, they gave me some Hershey bars.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The kids went out and bought some Hershey bars because I talked about Hershey bars.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- or one of the schools, I'm not sure which one it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that night, that city get bombed again, all right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we could have been in that city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So again, we were saved, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The next day, we got on-- we got into the bus again, we drove to-- and at that time, we started to look the old man, the old soldier.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We gave him some cigarettes so he- we could do anything we want.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was one of those [NON-ENGLISH], the one day drafted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was like maybe 55, 60 or something, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So that's the kind of people at that time were-- [DRINKS] One thing happened one time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We are near Hamburg, also pull over at night because we're-- and-- and we're in a-- in a-- in a truck and there comes an SS division, Waffen-SS, you know, and with armored car.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this guy pulls right up next to us and stays there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we heard this-- you know, when they were there, we weren't allowed to go outside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't know we had the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
